title: Tony Travers on 2016, An Eventful Year In Politics
itunes:author: Tony Travers and Emma Rees
description: Contributor(s): Tony Travers and Emma Rees | Professor Tony Travers discusses the key political events of 2016, an unprecedented year in politics which saw the UK vote for Brexit and Donald Trump elected US President.
